    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash, then cut your <strong>pak choi </strong>in half, separating the <strong>white base</strong> and <strong>green tops</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p>",
